<i>verb</i>: 잠수하다 [잠수하다], 잠그다 [잠그다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>잠수하다 [잠수하다]</dt><br>
<dd>submerge; go underwater</dd><br>
<dd>물속에 몸 전체가 잠기도록 들어가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To go into water so that one's body is completely covered with water.</dd><br>
<dt>잠그다 [잠그다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sink; submerge</dd><br>
<dd>액체 속에 넣거나 가라앉게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To put something in a liquid or make it go down to the bottom of the liquid.</dd><br>
<dd>2. invest; sink</dd><br>
<dd>앞날을 보고 재물을 들이다.</dd><br>
<dd>To put one's money into something for the future.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>